node.text:
Our Re/CASETiFY Technology in action. 🌀⁠
⁠
Now for the first time, we are making products from the cases collected via the RECASETiFY recycling program.⁠
We infuse broken down cases with manufacturing plastic scraps & plant-derived bio-plastics, to give them a second life. Only at #CASETiFY. ♻️⁠
⁠
Explore the Re/CASETiFY Collection for iPhone 13 ♻️ #ReCASETiFY

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CASETiFY on September 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and phone.

node.text:
🆕 iPhone 13 Cases are here and they’re Made to Protect!⁠
Introducing the NEW Re/CASETiFY Collection.⁠
⁠
Our Impact and Ultra Impact Crush Cases are powered by Re/CASETiFY Technology - combining used phone cases, manufacturing plastic scraps and plant-derived bio-plastic. The first of its kind Re/CASETiFY Technology creates cases made of 65% recycled materials! ♻️⁠
⁠
The new speckled bumpers in our Crush Cases are equipped with patented qitech™ 2.0 with military grade drop protection of up to 9.8ft. 💢⁠
⁠
Shop now only at #CASETiFY.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CASETiFY on September 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'WHAT DO WHATE WE MEAN BY SUSTAINABLE MATERIALS?'.

node.text: ♻️ 🌏 In progress: Making the planet a little bit cleaner and your case a little bit cuter. Sourcing innovative and greener alternatives to plastic has always been a mission here in CASETiFY. By making our products using ✔️100% compostable materials, ✔️biodegradable leather, ✔️recycled plastics. We divert waste from landfills and eliminate the need for using single-use plastic. Swipe to find out more. #DropToZero⁠⁠⁠

node.text: Show your love to mother nature with our latest artist, @annupton.art from “No Planet B" collection. Fueled by sun and sand, this colorful collection has a mixture of white sandy beaches, Hawaiian sunsets, and colorful waves. Explore the whole collection now, only at #CASETiFY.

💚🌱 Show your love and dedication to our planet with this energizing tropical leaf abstract by @ettavee, her artwork was inspired by life in France, travel adventures, tropical settings, colorful fruit and pop culture. Huge impact starts with small steps, by switching your tech accessories to a greener option, with our 100% compostable phone cases. After all, there’s #NoPlanetB #DropToZero⁠⁠

At CASETiFY, we care for you and our planet. 🌏 To show our love and support for #TheresNoPlanetB, we have brought 6 artists together to use their creativity to make a difference by showing positive changes to our environment. 🌱 ⁠
⁠
Our new “No Planet B” Collection  ranges from floral to nature prints on our ultra compostable cases which is 100% compostable, made with plant based material and printed with eco-friendly soy ink. ♻️ Let's join forces to make our world a better place. #DropToZero⁠
